### 1️⃣ Register a New Student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "phone": "9876543210",
    "password": "SecurePass123"
}

### 2️⃣ Login with Registered User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "NewSecurePass123"
}

### 3️⃣ Send OTP for Password Reset
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com"
}

### 4️⃣ Verify OTP (Replace `123456` with actual OTP received)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "otp": "123456"
}
### 5️⃣ Reset Password after OTP Verification
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "otp": "123456",
    "newPassword": "NewestSecurePass123"
}

